        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Situation B. Amber’s Claim</strong></p><p>Amber was working on the chip board and notices a pattern.</p><p><u>Amber’s Claim: </u></p><p>If you have the same number of black chips as red chips, the value is 0. For example, I can write this as +5 + –5 = 0. </p><p><strong>1.  </strong>Do you agree with her reasoning? Explain.</p>"
          ]
        }
