          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Situation C. Nadie Needs Help</strong></p><p>Nadie’s Situation</p><p>I was also analyzing moves on the chip board for the game. I have a chip board with 4 red chips. I need to subtract 2 black chips, but there are no black chips on the board. It is impossible to subtract 2 black chips. There are none on the board!</p><p>What can Nadie do to the chip board so that she can subtract 2 black chips? Explain your reasoning.</p>"
          ]
        }
